### STEP 1: First login to get a fresh token
POST http://localhost:7070/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

### STEP 2: Copy the token from above response and paste it below
### Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with the actual token value (without quotes)

@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get top candidate by popularity score
# Returns candidate with highest average skill popularity
GET http://localhost:7070/api/reports/candidates/top-by-popularity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get top candidate without authentication (should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:7070/api/reports/candidates/top-by-popularity
